msgid "Notes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.random.mtrand.RandomState:55
msgid ""
"The Python stdlib module \"random\" also contains a Mersenne Twister pseudo-"
"random number generator with a number of methods that are similar to the "
"ones available in `RandomState`. `RandomState`, besides being NumPy-aware, "
"has the advantage that it provides a much larger number of probability "
"distributions to choose from."
msgstr ""

